# Phase React-1: Transform "Shop by Print" to Use print_type Column

**Purpose:** Transform the backend functionality of "Shop by Print" dropdown to dynamically fetch print categories from the `print_type` column in the `products` table instead of relying on a separate `prints` table. This phase focuses exclusively on backend data source transformation without any UI/UX changes.

**Target Outcome:** The "Shop by Print" dropdown remains visually and functionally identical but now sources print categories directly from product data, ensuring automatic updates when new print types are added to products.

**Critical Constraint:** ⚠️ **ZERO UI/UX CHANGES** - The navbar placement, dropdown styling, mobile menu layout, and all visual elements MUST remain exactly as they are. This phase only modifies the data fetching logic.


